dct_description_sm: This line data layer represents roads for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2001. The dataset was originally published by the Portage County Planning and Zoning Department in 2001.[The Centerline data set is a vector representation of center of pavement in the County of Portage, Wisconsin. The centerlines are digitized from 1:12000 digital orthophotography or entered by coordinate geometry.]
